<center><h1>Hey! Test your football instincts!</h1>
<p><h3>Think you can predict winners just by looking at the teams? Try your choices without spending a penny !</h3></p>
<p><h5>
	EPL Bets brings to you an opportunity to showcase your prediction capabilites in the highly competitive English Premier League matches. 
	Forecast winners like a pundit before the match starts, and win yourself respect among other fellow punters.
</h5></p>
<br/>
<div class="row">
	<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
		<%= button_to "Show Matches", matches_path, class: "btn btn-primary", method: :get %>
	</div>
	
	<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
	<%= button_to "View Leaderboard", leaderboard_path, class: "btn btn-success", method: :get %>
	</div>
	
	<% if current_user %>
		<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
			<%= button_to "My Bets", show_user_bets_path, class: "btn btn-danger", method: :get %>
		</div>
		
		<% if current_user.admin == true %>
		<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
			<%= button_to "Add Match", new_match_path, class: "btn btn-primary", method: :get %>
		</div>
		<% end %>
	<% end %>
</div>
<br/>
<p>
	<h5><b>Odds on upcoming matches are decided anytime after the previous gameweek and 48 hours before the current 
	gameweek starts. Odds once decided are not subjected to change to ensure uniformity. Default odds are 1 for all teams
	whose odds are not yet updated. </b></h5>
</p>
</center>